<div class="container marketing">
    
    <div class="row featurette">
        <h3 class="featurette-heading">
        Game Night is your one-stop site to find fellow gamers looking to play or watch the same games as you!  
        </h3>
        <p class="lead">
        Are you tired of sitting in game lobbies with strangers and griefers?  Are you tired of wishing you had someone new to play
        an amazing new boardgame with?  Are you tired of wishing you had someone to just throw the ball back to you?
        </p>
    </div>


    <div class="row featurette">
        <p class="lead">
        This site was made for you and exists solely to add to your enjoyment of the games we all love.  Videogames, boardgames,
        live sports, backyard games, whatever it may be, this is the place to find a teammate, group, clan, or human target!
        
        Whether you're looking for a party for the newest AAA game, or a co-op partner for a retro game, this is the place.  Find players
        on the same platform to help with your difficult missions.  Find mentors to teach the ins and outs of crafting, or survivor squads
        and stats.  Help a noob out with a steep learning curve or a total lack of tutorial missions.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>